Class Variant

java.lang.Object
  fs.polyglot.model.TreeObject
      fs.polyglot.model.PolyglotString
          fs.polyglot.model.Variant

public class Variant
extends PolyglotString

This class implements a tree object representing a variant. It has as properties its path, its string UID, a Language object and the actual string. As subtype of PolyglotString, it is always considered complete, since there are no subnodes. Two variants are considered equal, if they have the same path, stringID and languageID. The value is irrelevant, since only the abstract position in the string tree is considered.

Author:
Simon Hampe
